sci_fi_action.title: Sci-Fi Action
sci_fi_action.description: Laser swords, laser knives, laser daggers and more!

283992.title: Redline
283992.description: In this animated high-speed thrill, a daredevil driver and his secret love face off in the most dangerous and exciting car race in the universe.

284009.title: Turbulent Skies
284009.description: A pilot-less plane malfunctions midflight, and the military threatens to destroy it before it crashes—but the one man who can fix it is on the ground.

287458.title: Ghidorah, the Three-Headed Monster
287458.description: After a meteorite unleashes a three-headed beast upon Tokyo, Mothra tries to unite with Godzilla and Rodan to battle the extraterrestrial threat.

287498.title: Godzilla Raids Again
287498.description: Godzilla battles an irradiated Ankylosaur and destroys Osaka in the process.

289816.title: Ghost In The Shell
289816.description: See the groundbreaking original before the release of the live-action remake starring Scarlett Johansson! It is 2029 and a female cyborg hunts a hacker who robs humans of their memories.

300846.title: The Wraith
300846.description: A mysterious black turbo racing car appears and challenges a murderous gang leader to a series of races. The driver's identity may surprise everyone.

324872.title: Wasteland
324872.description: When a group of religious zealots destroy everything that he loves and leaves him for dead, a man embarks on a journey of post-apocalyptic revenge.

326591.title: Big Bad Bugs
326591.description: When several American soldiers suddenly vanish, the special ops team sent to find them encounter a group of giant extraterrestrial insects instead.

326989.title: Weaponized
326989.description: A detective doubts the guilt of a veteran accused of a mass shooting and uncovers a dangerous military operation with unimaginable consequences.

342032.title: 10.0 Earthquake
342032.description: As a series of earthquakes tear apart LA, Emily and Jason race through the ruined city, diverting the epicenter, in hopes of saving millions of lives.

364436.title: Arachnicide
364436.description: The L9 Commando task force is called to destroy an incubator used for a drug operation but soon realize it has created giant spiders.

367625.title: 2010: Moby Dick
367625.description: In this reimagining of the classic novel, an unhinged submarine captain searches fanatically for the prehistoric whale that took his leg.

367633.title: 500 MPH Storm
367633.description: In this tale of man vs. nature, one man must save his family after an experiment gone wrong unleashes deadly hurricanes capable of destroying America.

367653.title: American Warships
367653.description: It's up to the crew of the USS Iowa to stop global disaster and save humanity when a mysterious fleet of ships launches an attack against Earth.

367721.title: Mega Shark VS Kolossus
367721.description: The world must figure out how to stop a mega shark and a Cold War-era giant robot doomsday device before they destroy everything on land and sea.

367793.title: Megafault
367793.description: After a mining explosion causes a massive earthquake, it’s up to a miner and a seismologist to save the U.S. from further destruction.

367805.title: Road Wars
367805.description: After the earth's water supply is depleted, a breed of blood-drinking humans force survivors to contend with a whole new threat to their existence.

367806.title: San Andreas Quake
367806.description: When no one listens to her warnings about a colossal earthquake, an L.A. scientist races to save her family before the city breaks from the mainland.

382248.title: Asteroid: Final Impact
382248.description: Nobody believes a disgraced whistleblower scientist who detects a giant asteroid barreling toward Earth leaving him alone to save the planet.

385501.title: Cyborg 2
385501.description: In the year 2074, the PinWheel corporation creates a cyborg designed to charm her way into a rival manufacturer's headquarters and then self-detonate.

389845.title: Rollerball
389845.description: In the future, the world's favorite sport is the extremely violent Rollerball. Can the game's most popular player show his naysayers who's boss?

416202.title: Haunters
416202.description: One day, a man with supernatural power comes into a small pawn shop Gyu-nam works and begins to control people’s mind to rob the place. The man is utterly surprised when he realizes that his supernatural power doesn’t work on Gyu-nam. Flustered, the man ends up killing a man by accident and his murder is recorded on the security camera. From then on, the man begins to hunt down Gyu-nam who holds critical evidence of his crime and Gyu-nam the man, for ruining his peaceful life. The unavoidable battle rages between an ordinary man and a man whose special power is rendered useless in the face of his only adversary.

418805.title: Jurassic City
418805.description: When rampaging raptors are unleashed from a top-secret lab, a black-ops unit is mobilized to contain the creatures before they cause chaos.

449365.title: Kung Fu Traveler
449365.description: A hostile alien race has overtaken Earth and humans are under attack with only one person who can fight the forces of the past to save the future.

449461.title: Disturbance
449461.description: A convicted serial killer must race against time as he defends the human race from transforming aliens who are fighting their own extinction.

449500.title: Dark Breed
449500.description: A terrible unknown evil may just have revealed itself after six active astronauts discover they have become infected by a strange, alien organism.

451360.title: Mars
451360.description: In the future, Mars has been colonized. A martial artist arrives to investigate what happened to his brother. A powerful mining company is the prime suspect.

451644.title: Geo-Disaster
451644.description: A family in Los Angeles are separated during a convergence of history's greatest disasters: a super volcano, a mega earthquake and a massive twister.

455818.title: A Mosquito Man
455818.description: A nuclear plant worker, abducted by an evil scientist in disguise, is exposed to rabid mosquito DNA, setting off revenge for all who wronged him.

456865.title: Creature
456865.description: A crack team of commandos are dispatched to a research lab, where they must fight for their lives against a genetically modified monstrosity.

456929.title: Redline
456929.description: When a murder victim is brought back to life through bionic technology, he tries to evade assassins as he seeks to avenge the one who betrayed him.

458533.title: RiffTrax: Future Force
458533.description: MSTK3 parodies the David Carradine classic about a bounty hunter who must protect a reporter from crooked cops, with the aid of a weaponized glove.

460302.title: Cyborg X
460302.description: After a radical weapons manufacturer is taken over by a cyber virus, a group of survivors must fight to save humanity from an army of machines.

464214.title: The Lotus
464214.description: Alone in a post apocalyptic world, a woman meets a mysterious man who reveals a great deal of classified information that could save everyone.

466817.title: Future Kick
466817.description: Set in the future, where a sinister corporation sells black market body parts, it takes an armed kickboxer to take them on and restore law and order.

466920.title: Warlords of the 21st Century
466920.description: A mysterious biker rises from the ashes of World War III to protect a peace-loving community from an outlaw leader's gas-guzzling war machine.

467937.title: Perfect Weapon
467937.description: When an authoritarian government sends assassins to kill enemies of the state, a top hitman makes a discovery that makes him reconsider his loyalties.

468457.title: Fallout
468457.description: When Russian forces seize a NASA space station, a defiant pilot and his crew set out on an experimental ship to stop them and quash a nuclear threat.

468930.title: The Precipice
468930.description: In a post-apocalyptic world, an ex-soldier and her prisoner traverse enemy territory to locate a place that holds the key to their nation’s salvation.

468972.title: Warriors of the Apocalypse
468972.description: After World War 3, a fierce group of female warriors fights mutant scavengers and rogue renegades while evading a dictator’s evil bounty hunters.

468975.title: Eruption LA
468975.description: A struggling screenwriter working on a disaster movie faces the real thing when a series of volcanoes explode all over Los Angeles.

473896.title: Apocalypse Rising
473896.description: A teen with mind-powers flees a planet with her warriors after a war of the undead. When they land on Earth, war breaks out again and the undead rise.

475833.title: Solar Destruction
475833.description: When a math prodigy discovers a new way of predicting solar flares, he tries to warn of an impending catastrophe, but no one in power will listen.

475994.title: Reptisaurus
475994.description: When a group of friends get stranded on a seemingly deserted island, they soon realize that there is another inhabitant who is not exactly friendly.

478727.title: Pandemic
478727.description: A virus tears through New Mexico. A local veterinarian teams up with an eccentric rancher to expose the true threat and save mankind.

479886.title: Antibody
479886.description: A terrorist houses a nuclear bomb detonator inside his body. A security expert races against time to track down and destroy it, before it’s too late.

479907.title: Blue Demon
479907.description: Military scientists see their top-secret experiment go very wrong, when the sharks they are training escape from the lab and go on a feeding frenzy.

480213.title: Dark Waters
480213.description: When unusually vicious sharks attack an oil rig in the Gulf of Mexico, a team goes to investigate, as the bloodthirsty creatures prowl for human prey.

484023.title: Dead Rising: Endgame
484023.description: Reporter Chase Carter must stop a secret government conspiracy aimed at ending a zombie epidemic but will also kill millions of innocent civilians.

486433.title: The Last Starship
486433.description: Conflict and tension looms heavily across the broken remains of a distant, post-apocalyptic world.

486707.title: Virtual Combat
486707.description: After a scientist brings virtual reality characters to life, a human cop must defeat an evil warrior while saving two VR women from a cybersex game.

486868.title: Miami Magma
486868.description: Follows prodigy vulcanologist Antoinette Vitrini and her sister Emily as they attempt to blow the whistle on an illegal oil drilling scheme before it sets off the eruption of a super-volcano directly beneath Miami.

487951.title: Earthstorm
487951.description: A massive asteroid's impact on the moon shifts its orbit, causing massive storms on earth due to the sudden changes in ocean tides.

488330.title: Dragon Fighter
488330.description: An experimental DNA-sampled clone of an alleged fire-breathing dragon escapes a military base and a security guard must battle the destructive beast.

489704.title: Project: Human Weapon
489704.description: When a supersoldier with psychic and telekinetic abilities vanishes from a government lab, a black ops agent is assigned to find and terminate him.

491327.title: Trancers 5: Sudden Deth
491327.description: Future lawman Jack Deth must find his way home from the other-dimensional world of Orpheus, where magic works and trancers are the ruling class.

493142.title: Ba'al: The Storm God
493142.description: A fatally-ill archaeologist embarks on a daring adventure, hoping to cure his cancer by retrieving the ancient amulets of a powerful local deity.

493214.title: Flashburn
493214.description: A man who is the only one who knows the cure for a global and deadly virus finds himself sealed off in a warehouse after a car crash with no memory.

495446.title: The City of Gold
495446.description: A bereaved media magnate joins his ex-girlfriend on a philanthropic mission to the Peruvian Amazon and instead discovers danger and dark secrets.

496364.title: Terror Beneath the Sea
496364.description: Two reporters covering torpedo tests investigate the sighting of an underwater creature and soon become prisoners of fish-men in an underwater city.

497286.title: Nemesis 3:  Prey Harder
497286.description: The third installment in the Nemesis saga finds Alex fighting cyborg mercenaries in 1998 East Africa while evading capture by Central Command in 2077.

497327.title: Dragon Wasps
497327.description: A scientist joins with the U.S. army in the jungles of Belize to find her father and has to deal with war crossfire and flame-shooting giant wasps.

500502.title: District C-11
500502.description: Two fearless rookie cops get assigned to a lethal district of constant gunfire after the world is placed under military rule and law.

502233.title: Descenso (Doblado)
502233.description: When Earth’s Ring of fire starts overheating, with unprecedented volcanic activity, a team of scientists gathers to prevent a global catastrophe.

504555.title: Absolute Aggression
504555.description: A business mogul creates a virtual reality prison where inmates must use their minds to defeat a labyrinth of games, or die trying.

506334.title: Termination Man
506334.description: A technologically enhanced special agent is tasked with the mission of stopping a ruthless terrorist, who is in possession of a powerful toxic gas.

506700.title: Atomic Twister
506700.description: When tornadoes hit a nuclear power plant, catastrophe is unleashed on a small town. Can anyone stop this path of destruction before it’s too late?

509101.title: Deadman Apocalypse
509101.description: In an apocalyptic future, a team of military ops is sent on a harrowing mission to retrieve water stolen by the inhabitants of an underground world.

517420.title: End of the World
517420.description: Natural disasters tear apart Los Angeles, as a father and daughter attempt to evade the solar storms, tsunamis, volcanoes, and flooding.

519982.title: Grace Is Gone
519982.description: Survivors in menacing, post-epidemic world fight daily battles with dangerous gangs, as they attempt to make it through another day.

520024.title: Iron Thunder
520024.description: A corrupt colonel steals a newly developed military tank powered by human thought, as he prepares to attack Las Vegas. Can he be stopped?

521921.title: Mantera
521921.description: A security breach at a technology company results in a clueless college student gaining a motorbike, which allows him to turn into a lethal weapon.

526470.title: Robowar
526470.description: After a team of fearless commandos accept a jungle rescue mission, they discover they’re being hunted by a murderous robotic creature.

526831.title: The Amazing Bulk
526831.description: Meet Henry Howard, a scrappy young scientist who tests an experimental serum which turns him into the Bulk, a destructive and powerful creature.

526969.title: Terra Formars
526969.description: When 21st-century scientists seed Mars with algae and roaches to help the toxic atmosphere, a mission flight there disappears and a new ship must go.

532048.title: Steampunk Samurai Biker Chick
532048.description: In 2165, a post-apocalyptic San Francisco is on fire as soldiers battle invaders and looters drain the city of its life-sustaining fuel and water.

533300.title: Revenge Quest
533300.description: In 2031, a dangerous inmate escapes from a Martian prison colony and travels to Los Angeles to seek revenge on those responsible for his imprisonment.

535044.title: Empire of Ash II
535044.description: “New Idaho,” 2050. The few survivors of a deadly virus that has laid waste to the human race fight for their freedom against the new evil empire.

535048.title: Fatal Conflict
535048.description: In post-apocalyptic Los Angeles, a disgraced ex-pilot gets a shot at redemption by helping the governor prevent a spaceship from flattening the city.

535058.title: Last Stand
535058.description: What’s left of civilization after a world war is in the hands of an ex-con warrior who must stop a dictator with access to the U.S. nuclear arsenal.

539674.title: Independence Daysaster
539674.description: When Earth is attacked by hostile aliens, a firefighter and a rogue scientist team up to build the only weapon capable of defeating the attackers.

546229.title: Abduction
546229.description: A SWAT team member with both amnesia and a kidnapped daughter works with a hitman whose wife was abducted to find the culprits behind the crimes.

549626.title: Mutant War
549626.description: In this ‘Galaxy Destroyer’ sequel, a surviving hero fights tribes and monsters while helping to keep a group of sisters from being bred by mutants.

550641.title: Fire From Below
550641.description: The hunt for an alternative energy source unleashes a toxic lithium that reaches the earth's surface, setting off a devastating series of events.

552228.title: Magma: Volcanic Disaster
552228.description: A professor and his students try to convince the government and save Earth from impending Armageddon, after a giant comet triggers volcanic eruptions.

559467.title: Atomic Rulers (Atomic Rulers of the World)
559467.description: An outer space crimefighter known as Starman comes to Earth’s rescue when he learns that powerful criminals are threatening a nuclear winter.

559654.title: Invaders From Space
559654.description: A planetary gang of alien, amphibious men want to infect Earth with a lethal pandemic, a threat that doesn't sit well with the space fighter Starman.

561256.title: Thor: End of Days
561256.description: Norse god Thor chases the power-hungry Loki, but needs a female human’s aid, when he awakens on Earth without his mighty hammer or his memory.

570972.title: Dark Island
570972.description: When a defense contractor loses contact with its bioweapons lab on a remote island, a team of soldiers and scientists is sent to learn what happened.

571718.title: Neutron the Atomic Superman
571718.description: An evil scientist tries to harvest the brains of scientists who made a neutron bomb, a deadly pursuit that the powerful Neutron superman fights hard.

571747.title: Super Argo and the Faceless Giants
571747.description: After retiring from the wrestling ring, Colonel Superargo teams up with an Eastern mystic to stop an army of faceless robots from kidnapping athletes.

572441.title: Ultraman X the Movie
572441.description: Our team of superheroes faces off against a diabolical monster and its army of giant kaijus after a reality TV host steals a coveted precious gem.

574380.title: Transit 17
574380.description: In 2026, after a zombie plague has infected Europe, a team of resistance soldiers must protect a young girl who appears to hold the key to the cure.

582075.title: Monster Force Zero
582075.description: Armed with their new superpowers, a band of Sci-Fi cosplay pals enter the multiverse to defend Earth against alien forces bent on its destruction.

582788.title: Alien Agent
582788.description: When a gang of space invaders set their sights on conquering Earth, an intergalactic warrior must find a way to stop them from making landfall.

585640.title: 2025: The World Enslaved by a Virus
585640.description: In 2025, after Covid-19 ravaged the globe, a group of Christians fight back against the newly installed draconian worldwide regime left in its wake.

587321.title: Occupation
587321.description: When alien invaders threaten mankind, a group of random townspeople must band together and fight back against the vicious extraterrestrials.

588423.title: Rumble Strip
588423.description: When a former mercenary’s girlfriend is kidnapped, he must rescue her from the last dictator on Earth, who happens to be his own father.

589517.title: Immortal Combat: The Code
589517.description: A member of the 5 Elements clan becomes the most wanted man in the world when he’s injected with a secret code that could save humanity from disaster.

594961.title: Cyborg
594961.description: A cyborg on a quest to cure the world of a plague with a vaccine is captured by cannibals who plot to steal the antidote and rule the world.

598741.title: Absolute Force
598741.description: Agents are sent to retrieve a military weapon that has fallen into the wrong hands before it's used to destroy Earth.

605424.title: 2 Lava 2 Lantula
605424.description: Arrogant action star and slayer of lava-spewing spiders, Colton West, returns to save Florida and his step-daughter from a wave of arachnid terrorism.

606135.title: Virtually Dead
606135.description: Lured into a virtual reality game by an evil computer programmer, a group of gamers find themselves trapped in a fight for survival with the undead.

606516.title: RoboCop 3
606516.description: A heartless corporation kicks families out of their Motor City homes, inspiring RoboCop to bring his skills to a team of freedom fighters.

610579.title: Gamera: Super Monster
610579.description: With the earth on the brink of being enslaved by the evil alien Zanon, Gamera must battle monstrous foes from his past to save the planet once again.

610607.title: Gamera the Brave
610607.description: 23 years after Japan’s defending monster Gamera died in battle to save the continent, a young boy rescues an egg that will hatch the new Gamera.

612739.title: The Last Sentinel
612739.description: An electronically-enhanced soldier teams up with a fearless rebel fighter in humanity’s last line of defense against a deadly drone police force.

614171.title: The Protectors
614171.description: A young superhero finds out he shares DNA with aliens and joins a band of vigilantes to fight a powerful secret society’s plot for world domination.

616832.title: Enhanced
616832.description: In order to stop a mutant serial killer from hunting her down, a young woman with enhanced abilities must face impossible decisions to stop him.

618225.title: Danger Dolls
618225.description: A squad of four incredible female assassins travel between parallel universes to protect each world of humanity from evil forces out for dominion.

619919.title: Monster Island
619919.description: As the world tries to stop a giant kaiju bent on destruction, more and more monsters appear, each more terrible than the last, threatening humankind.

619920.title: Monster Hunters
619920.description: When an alien prison ship crashes in the California desert, it unleashes creature after creature. Can a  secret branch of the US government stop them?

619924.title: Collision Earth
619924.description: When a giant meteor threatens to destroy Earth, military protocols designed to stop the impact fail, and a team of scientists races to save humanity.

619927.title: Arctic Apocalypse
619927.description: When a massive influx of glacial melting spurs a new ice age in the Northern Hemisphere, a family must forge its way across frozen tundra to survive.

623024.title: Eclipse: The Rise of Ink
623024.description: Convinced he is destined to be a superhero, a fanboy puts together clues from predictions in a comic book to save New York City from imminent danger.

623858.title: Starforce
623858.description: A dutiful warrior and a beautiful ex-convict are stranded in an alien wasteland and left to fight the galaxy's most fearsome, otherworldly commandos.

624780.title: Apocalypse of Ice
624780.description: With a pandemic already underway, a scientist with the key to human survival has to survive a devastating polar vortex that has overtaken the globe.

627347.title: Terror of Mechagodzilla (Dubbed)
627347.description: When the Black Hole Aliens hatch a sinister scheme to unleash a robotic, laser-shooting monster on Tokyo, Godzilla is humanity’s only hope to stop it.

627349.title: Godzilla vs. Mechagodzilla (Dubbed)
627349.description: Godzilla finds himself in battle with his cosmic double bent on fulfilling an Okinawan prophecy warning of Earth's destruction at the monster’s claws.

627350.title: Godzilla vs. Megalon (Dubbed)
627350.description: In retaliation for the nuclear tests that razed their society, Seatopia sends a giant robot to destroy the world above that only Godzilla can defeat.

627351.title: Destroy All Monsters (Dubbed)
627351.description: Godzilla, Rodan, Mothra, and other monsters held in scientific captivity on a remote island are released by a race of she-aliens to conquer the world.

631191.title: Nautilus
631191.description: A group of survivors try to change the events that, over 100 years earlier, sent the world into the Dark Ages after mass destruction.

631544.title: Monsters of Man
631544.description: An illegal U.S. military op goes awry when killer robots are unleashed on heroin producers in Southeast Asia and end up wiping out an entire village.

637324.title: Cybernetic Showdown
637324.description: After an apocalypse, a group of powerful mutants threaten to destroy the last of humanity, until a vigilante swings in, ready to take them all down.

640990.title: Scavenger
640990.description: Welcome to a post-apocalyptic world, where an assassin must face her dark history, seeking revenge for a crime that changed her life.

647082.title: Doomsday
647082.description: Nearly 30 years after a deadly epidemic swept through Scotland, a commander and her crew search for an antidote when the virus emerges in London.

647775.title: Broken Darkness
647775.description: Sam and his friend Troy, along with a young woman, Rose, are thrust on a journey that takes them into the darkest parts of the underground world.

654144.title: Batwoman
654144.description: Batwoman must stop a madman, who has been kidnapping wrestlers with plans to create a new breed of man.

654292.title: Santo in the Wax Museum
654292.description: El Santo, the masked Mexican wrestler, investigates the kidnappings by a mysterious doctor who performs unnatural experiments on his victims.

654296.title: Santo in The Treasure of Dracula
654296.description: Santo gets his girlfriend to be the first to travel backwards in time to her past life.

654632.title: Dragon: The Weapon of God
654632.description: An underground group led by a teenager with amazing superherro powers fight back against a city police force bent on constant brutality.

657092.title: Land Shark
657092.description: Scientists attempting to create a cancer drug from a  genetically modified shark create a destructive killing machine that even they cannot control.

659446.title: Las Guerras Inmortales: Renacimiento (Doblado)
659446.description: En la guerra por la libertad, Trikalypse se alía con el líder de los rebeldes guerreros para acabar de una buena vez con la opresión de Dominion.

661882.title: SuperGrid
661882.description: In the apocalyptic near-future, a young smuggler is forced to convince his older brother to get back on the "Grid" and help him clear a debt.

665881.title: Godzilla vs. Gigan
665881.description: Suspicious of his employer, a manga artist assembles a team to investigate a garbled tape message while two kaijus launch their own plan of action.

666164.title: Bullets of Justice
666164.description: Two decades after the U.S. government’s secret World War III project to create a breed of super-soldiers, the “Muzzle” species rises to power.

667954.title: Ultraman Saga
667954.description: A decade and a half after Shin Asuka, the Earth has been taken over by the mysterious Alien Batt with only a few humans left fighting to survive.

671057.title: Omega Cop
671057.description: In a dystopic future amid environmental ruin, when the police are limited, one cop goes after a gang of slave traders.

671653.title: Mega Monster Battle: Ultra Galaxy: The Movie
671653.description: Three million light years from Earth on Planet M-78, Ultraman joins forces with allies to fight an army of giant monsters led by Ultraman Belial.

673672.title: Cold Fusion
673672.description: Alien technology falls into the hands of a mysterious terrorist organization that uses it to create a devastating weapon of mass destruction.

673673.title: Crystal Skulls
673673.description: It is 2020, and the apocalypse is inevitable. Only the 13th Skull can restore order before the Earth is destroyed from within by their power.

673685.title: Atomic Shark
673685.description: When a lifeguard catches wind of a dangerous anomaly off the coast of San Diego, she tasks a crew to assist her in saving it from destruction.

673686.title: Jet Stream
673686.description: A young scientist and a meteorologist team up to get to the bottom of what is causing these jet streams to level cities and bring down airplanes.

675099.title: Heatstroke
675099.description: Captain Stevie O’Bannon’s investigation into global warming reveals a well-designed plan of sabotage from a hoard of dinosaurs from an alien world.

675214.title: Death Race 2000
675214.description: In a dystopian future, an automobile race requires contestants to run down pedestrians to gain points that are tallied based on each kill's brutality.

680467.title: Dead Zone
680467.description: To stop the collapse of humanity, an elite team of soldiers must descend on a radiation-poisoned town and perform the ultimate stealth mission using high-tech armor and weapons.

681644.title: Revolt
681644.description: During an alien invasion, a stranded soldier suffering memory loss braves the Kenyan battlefield to find a resistance army and his true identity.

682052.title: Kill Mode
682052.description: In a dystopian gritty near future, a former freedom fighter tries to stop the company that owns the world from being shut down by dark secrets.

682175.title: Stonados
682175.description: When an unprecedented weather event puts the Eastern Seaboard under siege, a former storm chaser’s untested theory is the only chance of stopping it.

685615.title: Halo Legends
685615.description: The universe of the Halo video game series is expanded in seven short animated films from Japan's greatest anime directors and studios.

685617.title: Halo: The Fall of Reach
685617.description: Halo: The Fall of Reach follows the backstory of the shaping and creation of Spartan 117, The Master Chief.

685746.title: Super Tanker
685746.description: A damaged container ship is commissioned to transport an unstable and very deadly cold war artifact and release it into the deepest ocean trench.

688612.title: Super Eruption
688612.description: Yellowstone Park rangers Charlie and Kate come together to put a stop to one of the greatest natural disasters to ever threaten humanity.

690828.title: Python 2
690828.description: A businessman, his partner and his wife come to learn the unknown cargo they picked up from a Russian military base is a genetically-altered monster.

691330.title: Warbirds
691330.description: While carrying a small group of Allied soldiers and unknown cargo, a World War II pilot is forced to make an emergency landing in enemy territory.

691418.title: Exiled: The Chosen Ones
691418.description: When a man-made virus fails to kill the population, the government creates a game show where players are forced to kill each other for their freedom.

692134.title: The Prototype
692134.description: An agent is subjected to alien experimentation and wakes up 300 years into the future. With Earth now destroyed, he is the only hope for mankind.

693738.title: Snow Monster vs Ice Shark
693738.description: A gene research company sends a group into a mysterious snowy area on the edge of the Arctic where they get attacked by unknown giant creatures.

695214.title: Storm
695214.description: A meteorology professor sets out to derail his top-secret weather-manipulating invention after learning the military wants to use it as a weapon.

703913.title: Meltdown: Days of Destruction
703913.description: A scientist tries to protect his family after an experiment meant to destroy an asteroid instead shifts Earth's orbit closer to the sun.

708343.title: Meteor: First Impact
708343.description: A scientist races against the clock in an attempt to save Earth from a series of deadly meteor attacks.

710214.title: Invasion of the Mermaids
710214.description: When a mysterious water monster invades a fishing community on the South China Sea, it's up to a young man to protect his fiancé and the villagers.

711321.title: TMZ No BS: Hollywood's Biggest Lies
711321.description: TMZ dives into the biggest stories in hollywood. From the rise of Kim Kardashian to the fall of Jussie Smollett. Discover the true stories as the lies are brought to light.

712061.title: The Bronx Executioner
712061.description: A cyborg goes on a killing spree in a futuristic New York City where the Bronx is divided into rival zones controlled by humanoids and androids.

723452.title: The Mark
723452.description: A man implanted with a biometric computer chip, aka the Mark of the Beast, must keep it from falling into the wrong hands when the Rapture occurs.

723837.title: Alien Outpost
723837.description: In this pulse-pounding thriller, an elite unit of soldiers is charged with protecting a strategic outpost while under siege from an alien invasion.

724578.title: The Incredible Hulk Returns
724578.description: When a magical hammer summons The Mighty Thor, he joins forces with The Incredible Hulk for the first time to crush the forces of evil!

726075.title: Kill Order
726075.description: Uncanny abilities awaken within a troubled high school student when a tactical team arrives to abduct him for unknown reasons.

100000181.title: The Trial of the Incredible Hulk
100000181.description: When Dr. Banner is framed for a street crime, a blind attorney with his own vigilante identity takes his case and helps him chase an evil gangster.

04710.title: NightMan
04710.description: After being struck by lightning, a jazz musician gains the power to telepathically sense evil and becomes his city's nocturnal superhero.

03591.title: Chojin Sentai Jetman
03591.description: A freak accident leaves four unsuspecting humans with extraordinary powers. Now it's up to them to defend their dimension from villainous invaders.

0300005115.title: Kamen Rider: Kuuga
0300005115.description: Godai Yusuke must use a telepathic connection to transform into the warrior Kuuga and defend mankind from ferociously powerful monsters.

03504.title: Mirai Sentai Timeranger
03504.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! It's the 30th century and time travel is illegal. To help monitor and police time crimes, the Time Protection Department is founded. But when Don Dolnero and his nefarious gang manage to trick four new TPD cadets into allowing them travel to the 20th century, the four cadets are forced to pursue them for the sake of history. There, in a time foreign to them, the cadets enlist Tatsuya Asami, a young martial artist, to aid their mission. Together, these five youngsters become the Timerangers. And though they try to live as ordinary 20th-century citizens, the Timerangers dedicate their lives to stopping Dolnero and others that may follow in his footsteps, attempting to forever alter the proper timeline!

01072.title: Ultraman
01072.description: Hayata, one of the Science Patrol's members, holds the key to our salvation. Fate has given Hayata the ability to secretly transform into an amazing, super-powered giant from space. A being known as Ultraman!

0300009151.title: Ultraman Tiga
0300009151.description: A high-tech defense team protects Earth from monsters and alien invaders with the help of the giant super-being Ultraman Tiga.

0300008703.title: Captain America
0300008703.description: Superhero Captain America battles the evil arch villain known as "The Scarab" who harbors a secret device capable of destruction by sound.

03135.title: Kyuukyuu Sentai GoGoFive
03135.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! After the Bowzock, a ruthless-not to mention reckless- gang of interstellar biker thugs, destroy his home planet of Hazard, Dappu visits Earth where he discovers five humans with the ability to harness "Carmagic." With this power, these five heroes can defeat the Bowzock before the band of witless bikers is able to add Earth to its list of wrecked worlds.

0300006474.title: Ultraman Ace
0300006474.description: The Ultraman saga continues in this 1972 series that sees the new Ultraman Ace fight off the alien Yapool and his Terrible Monsters on planet Earth.

01795.title: Terraformars
01795.description: In the far future, humanity seeks to resolve Earth’s growing overpopulation problem by terraforming Mars as their second home. Five hundred years later, the United Nations Aeronautics and Space Administration sends out an expedition team to explore this new world. But an unintended side effect of the terraforming process has unleashed a horror no one could ever have imagined: the planet has become infested with Terraformars, man-sized cockroaches that prey on humans. Now humanity must bring together all its scientific resources and power to counter this monstrous threat, or face total extinction.

05.title: Transformers Energon
05.description: Years after "Transformers Armada", the Autobots continue to battle the Decepticons to prevent the resurrection of Unicron.

02180.title: Chouriki Sentai Ohranger
02180.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! It is the year 1999. The Machine Empire of Baranoia, led by Emperor Bacchus Wrath, has invaded Earth with the intention of wiping out all human life and bringing about machine rule. Chief Counsellor Miura of the UAOH (United Airforce Overtech Hardware), in a desperate attempt to quell this invasion, has revived super energies born of the lost civilization of Pangaea. Enlisting an elite squad of the finest officers the UAOH has to offer, Miura has harnessed Tetrahedron Power, granting the team the power to transform into the Ohrangers, and save humanity from its darkest crisis yet!

021.title: Transformers: Prime
021.description: Roll out with all-new adventures starring Optimus Prime, Bumblebee, Arcee, and the rest of the heroic Autobots as they battle the evil Decepticons! Now that big bad Megatron has returned to Earth, Team Prime prepares for an epic struggle to save the planet. Meanwhile, the Autobots have to guard Jack, Miko, and Raf, three kids who've accidentally discovered them. Intense drama, heavy metal action, awesome animation--it's all here, bigger and better than ever!

0300009149.title: Ultraman Dyna
0300009149.description: The Year: 2017. Humanity has built settlements throughout the solar system to begin the conquest of unknown lands.

02409.title: Ultraman Leo
02409.description: Alien intergalactic slavers called Magma come to Earth in an attempt to find more slaves for their expanding evil empire. In response, the Ultra Warriors send Leo to protect the planet from this new threat.

04752.title: Ultraseven
04752.description: Ultra Guard and hero Ultraseven defend Earth from alien invaders in this classic sci-fi action series.

03853.title: Exploding Sun
03853.description: A spaceship with passengers, including the First Lady, makes a maiden voyage to the moon, but a violent solar storm sends it hurtling toward the sun.

0300008056.title: Kamen Rider Zero-One
0300008056.description: The action series about a young man on his bike heading to an amusement park who doesn’t know he’ll become a cyborg crimefighter for the ages.

04750.title: Ultraman Geed
04750.description: The story of a teenager who inherits the evil Ultraman's genes, but never loses sight of friendship and a strong will to become a true hero.

02061.title: World Trigger
02061.description: With superhuman technology at their fingertips, Yuma and Osamu must work together to defend their new reality against unknown beings.

010.title: Transformers: Armada
010.description: It's up to Optimus and the Autobots to stop Megatron from turning all robots on Earth into Decepticons with the Allspark!

02927.title: Gekisou Sentai Carranger
02927.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! After the Bowzock, a ruthless-not to mention reckless- gang of interstellar biker thugs, destroy his home planet of Hazard, Dappu visits Earth where he discovers five humans with the ability to harness "Carmagic." With this power, these five heroes can defeat the Bowzock before the band of witless bikers is able to add Earth to its list of wrecked worlds.

04106.title: Ninpuu Sentai Hurricaneger
04106.description: After tragedy strikes on graduation day at the Ninja Academy, three pupils waste no time taking on the clan of evil space warriors responsible.

04751.title: Ultraman Orb
04751.description: A hero battles extraterrestrial threats with the power of the Orb Ring which turns him into a warrior of light, Ultraman Orb.

02406.title: Wild C.A.T.S.
02406.description: The benevolent race known as the Wild C.A.T.s (Covert Action Team), are fearless, super-powered warriors sworn to defeat the evil Daemonites, who seek to dominate planet Earth.

0539.title: Beast Wars
0539.description: On pliocenic Earth, the heroic Maximals and the evil Predacons battle for survival against each other and against a violent planet.

0300009482.title: Ring of Fire
0300009482.description: An oil rig triggers volcanic eruptions across the globe that could mean the end of humanity if a young activist can't stop the ripple effect.

0300006348.title: Ultraman Orb the Origin Saga
0300006348.description: In this origins series from the Ultraman universe comes the tale of two young men whose friendship and quest for greatness turns into a bitter feud.

0300006353.title: Return of Ultraman
0300006353.description: The 1971 TV series featuring the original superhero Ultraman and Ultraseven as they protect earth from a new attack by aliens and monsters.

02308.title: Denji Sentai Megaranger
02308.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! When his video game prowess is discovered by I.N.E.T., high school student Kenta Date is brought in to lend his expertise to their mysterious research. Meanwhile, four classmates show up, wanting to know more about the I.N.E.T. facility. Their experience will change their lives forever, as I.N.E.T. survives an attack by the nefarious Dr. Hinelar and an army from another dimension determined to conquer our reality!
